import { HttpErrorResponse } from '@angular/common/http'; import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { Game } from './game'; import { NbaService } from './nba.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-root', templateUrl: './app.component.html', styleUrls: ['./app.component.css'] }) export class AppComponent implements OnInit { constructor(private nbaService : NbaService){} title = 'NBA-APP'; public Games!: Game[]; ngOnInit(){ this.getGames(); console.log(this.Games) } public getGames():void{ this.nbaService.getLiveGames().subscribe( (response: Game[])=>{this.Games=response; console.log(response)}, (error:HttpErrorResponse)=>{alert(error);} ); } }
